Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two people's deductions and suspense\Nfill the gulf between love and hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shining stages of Broadway!{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A big case with Ran and my mom!{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After we solved the case in Yokohama's Chinatown, Ran suddenly collapsed.{USO/TMS}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In her delirium, she remembered a case from the past.{TMS}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was when my mom convinced us to attend a musical in New York.{USO/TMS}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In front of the theatre, Mom's old friend, the famous actress Sharon Vineyard, was waiting.{USO/TMS}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was going to give us a backstage tour, but as we walked through the wings before the show...{TMS}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The costumes for the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're up there so they won't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Ran...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost there...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost at the hospital...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You okay, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Someone... someone's after my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so... The rope must have broken since it's so old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, who put such an old armor up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it could've been worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're lucky that large mirror wasn't broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's our guardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, you two. You shouldn't be thanking a mirror or any god.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be thanking{\i1} her{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you! You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, we need to get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll see you after the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cut myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, do I have a bandage...{TMS}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it, there's no such thing as God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If God existed, this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going home, Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not staying to watch the play, Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was planning to, but I've got business elsewhere.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it looks like a storm is rising.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I think I'll pass.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't see shows like {\i1}this{\i0} in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But {\i1}someone{\i0} doesn't seem to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! At least try to pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so interesting about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All they did was turn a Greek myth into a romantic comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what Greek myth is this based on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Golden Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, there were three goddesses: Hera, Athena and Aphrodite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were invited to a banquet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but Eris, who wasn't invited,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,got jealous and sent the three a golden apple with a message...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"For the Fairest."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the three goddesses decided that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the prince of Troy should choose who should get the apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each of them tried to bribe him with promises if he picked her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the guy we met before is playing the unfortunate prince of Troy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The actress playing the wife of the rich man is Zeus' wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hera, the goddess of matrimony who promised him he'd be the world's most powerful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Japanese-looking actress with a lot of character is Athena,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the goddess of wisdom who promised him victory in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that sexy actress is the goddess of beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aphrodite, who promised him the world's most beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the one in the last scene with the grim look, who was jealous of the other three
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is the one who gave them the golden apple: Eris, the goddess of strife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this version of the story, the rich lady offers the guy money,{MIYAKI-loose}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the smart lady offers him a great job,{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the babe offers him a date,{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the golden apple has been changed{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to a jewelled apple-shaped necklace.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So who did the prince choose?{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aphrodite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to legend, that's how the Trojan War got started.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's the Greek myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This musical is quite different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you see the prince's identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...you're going to be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Behold, sinful humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Michael!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michael? The archangel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kiddin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carefully listen to my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heath...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me this isn't happening...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right... This must be a joke...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. It's not a joke. It's a murder!{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A handgun...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was shot with a handgun?{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what it looks like.{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should probably evacuate too.{TMS/MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, take care of Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Figured I wouldn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A bullet casing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good Lord!{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! Heath Flockheart!{MIYAKI-loose-ltil: "no way, the one who was shot was Heath Flockheart"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know him, Captain?{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife's a big fan of his.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what's the situation?{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've asked the actors to wait in their dressing rooms,{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but most of the audience has fled.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was shot straight in the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bullet's lodged into the wings in his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wings in his back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the bullet's entry wound, I'd say he was shot from a 40° angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,40°...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty sharp angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:46.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the killer was probably up on that terrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used a laser sight to aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Night Baroness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Yukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be watching the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no idea the musical would turn into a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was shot during the climax where the angel appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During that scene, smoke is released,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The actor is lifted while the projection in the mirror slides up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,making it look like he's emerging from the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's set up in a way to make it look real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So basically, the killer shot him from that terrace as he was rising from the mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, he threw the gun onto the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to cause a panic, and therefore be able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But are you sure about this? The killer being in the terrace, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course. Thanks to the smoke on-stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could clearly see a red beam of light pointing to the stage from the terrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My son saw it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Son?{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, he's standing right next to you.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is the son you're always talking about, Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, isn't he Yūsaku's spitting image?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're just as big pranksters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suspicious person reserved every seat in the terrace a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this person was wearing a scarf and hat, so we don't even know if it was a man or a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that must be the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why pick that seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't those seats expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:13:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The angle from that terrace isn't very good, so they're probably cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's easy to leave an impression if someone with their face hidden asks for an entire area,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which is exactly what the killer wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are these two strange marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in the neck. Doesn't it look like a burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's blood in his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could the blood be from grabbing his chest after he was shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is that it's smudged, like someone tried to clean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have touched his hand somewhere after it got bloody,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there's nothing in his clothes, nor is there anything he could've touched in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, has the Night Baroness solved this mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ehh... Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not ask Yūsaku? I bet he'd have some ideas.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Yūsaku's locked in a hotel room in LA, working.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a shame. A celebrity murdered,{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I don't have a single lead.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be hearing it from the public, the commish{commissioner} {\i1}and{\i0} my wife...{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then maybe Shin'ichi might be able to solve it?{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just a kid, he's never investigated a real murder before.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he solved a case while we were on the plane.{MIYAKI/USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sure after the crook was caught he told you he'd known who it was all along.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He loves to brag...{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he was involved in the investigation from the very start.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was?{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He lined up all the suspects and told them how it happened with that smug look of his.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Holmes or Poirot.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? The killer's one of the four actresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right as this case took place, I ran over to the terrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found a bullet casing, but it wasn't hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This proves someone planted it in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you saw it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A laser sight's red light coming from the terrace to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we can't know which it was coming from or which it was aimed at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That laser sight was probably aimed not from the terrace, but from the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:16:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to make us believe the gunshot came from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the masked person purchasing the tickets, and the strange present
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,were just a ruse to lead us to suspect someone was threatening the actresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, this is part of the trick, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is where that armor fell before the play started, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look carefully at the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a fishing line tied to a nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And next to it, there's a mark, as if something had been cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the fishing line was attached to the armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then someone did it intentionally?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The killer probably had a knife or similar in his shoe, and used it to cut the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,bringing down the armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:17:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer knew that we, Sharon's friends, would come this way during the guided tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that the killer is one of those who was with us when the armor fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as well as one of the actresses who was on-stage with Heath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, she could aim the laser sight at the terrace, as well as shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the four goddesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Heath is six foot three.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could any of those women shoot {\i1}down{\i0} at him?{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, he was behind that mirror!{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! How, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er... I haven't figured that out yet.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that true, Lila?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heath and I were dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For about five years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you were dating my boyfriend behind my back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be talking about this in a day like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be the angriest of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since your boyfriend apparently had two others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then... Rose too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were dating him too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently all four had a motive for killing Heath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand that he was involved with all three, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What reason does Everith have?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike the other three, she doesn't have a photo of him on her mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, Heath and Everith were married.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:19:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sharon told me while we were touring around the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They kept it secret even from the other actresses, in case it might affect their popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why she kept glaring at him when he was flirting with the others...{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But right now, we have to figure out how the killer shot him from that height.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rose was the closest one to the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she was acting as if she'd collapsed from seeing the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everith was sitting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Akane was on her knees as if praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who could shoot from the highest was Lila who was standing and holding her head,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but unlike the other three, her hands weren't hidden by the smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:47.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People would've noticed if she'd pulled out a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could Heath have been crouching?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those wings were bound to his feet, making it completely impossible for him to crouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin'ichi? Have you thought of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You thought of something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you came up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran.{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:27.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How tall are you?{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,160 cm.{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, five foot three...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This pamphlet is about 12 inches tall, or one foot...{USO/MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you put this on your head and stand in front of the mirror for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to prove with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:20:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A crack...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:20:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kizu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A crack?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a tiny crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd. This mirror's been with the theater for years, and was their guardian angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and they'd supposedly get bad luck if they broke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what Sharon said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like they glued it together. Were they {\i1}really{\i0} taking care of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this curtain look a bit twisted?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe somebody ran into it when trying to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Shin'ichi, let's get back. Your mom's going to kill us...{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did it get stuck in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This flip door isn't used for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:00.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.82,0:22:03.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see. I understand it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:08.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The killer used this stage's tricks to commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:15.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A bloody murder, committed by someone as crafty as the goddess Eris.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From those positions, you four couldn't have shot him from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who turned off the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the killer made use of something in the stage.{something taken out here}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the killer's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.45,0:24:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only one person could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan: Shin'ichi Kudo's New York Case (Case Closed)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.49,0:24:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,新一「蘭、次回のヒントなんかすんげぇムカツク・・・(--メ)」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.83,0:24:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,蘭「野生の勘ってやつ？」
